        {
            "title": "川普在白宮記者晚宴槍擊事件後安全撤離",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 週六晚間,一場備受矚目的活動因緊急安全事件而突然中斷,白宮記者晚宴現場陷入混亂。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">唐納德·川普總統讚揚聯邦安全人員在週六晚間白宮記者晚宴緊急疏散後的快速反應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">總統在社交媒體上發表聲明,確認執法部門已逮捕造成此次事件的涉事人員,儘管這起事件令首都進入高度警戒狀態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">活動現場的影片捕捉到,在會場內傳出巨大爆炸聲響後,包括唐納德·川普總統在內的與會者被迫尋找掩護的瞬間。進一步細節顯示,白宮發生了涉及槍手的事件。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a656e25d-0405-3c94-b84e-71ae48f72f7a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特勤局特工立即包圍總統,在安全協議啟動後迅速將他從宴會廳護送至安全地點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>安全協議啟動及後續措施</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">總統讚揚現場警員的英勇表現,指出戰術反應成功化解威脅,未進一步升級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管此次安全漏洞嚴重,川普在事件發生後立即表示希望維持正常狀態,告訴其追隨者:\"我建議’讓活動繼續進行’,但將完全遵從執法部門的指示。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這起事件在數百名記者、政治人物和名人中引發立即恐慌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">噪音的確切性質仍在調查中,但特勤局的快速反應凸顯了在當前重大地緣政治和國內緊張局勢期間,政府周圍的安全態勢已經提升。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>對行政穩定性的更廣泛影響</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次事件再次提醒人們,華盛頓目前籠罩著脆弱的氛圍。截至週六深夜,白宮尚未就干擾源頭或總統預定行程狀態提供具體細節。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場可能會密切關注政府的任何官方聲明,因為政治領導層和國內穩定性的不確定性往往會在週日早盤交易中波及更廣泛的風險偏好情緒。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著首都保持高度警戒,投資者將關注事件的進一步澄清。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%99%9A%E5%AE%B4%E6%A7%8D%E6%93%8A%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%BE%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%92%A4%E9%9B%A2-020651588.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-26 10:35:46",
